casebody.data:
RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2004-1993. Ohio Consumers’ Counsel v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, Nos. 03-2144-EL-AAM, 03-2144-EL-ATA and 03-2144-EL-UNC. Reported at 109 Ohio St.3d 328, 2006-Ohio-2110, 847 N.E.2d 1184. On motion for reconsideration of FirstEnergy Corporation. Motion denied.

O’Connor and Lanzinger, JJ., dissent.

On motion to strike motion for reconsideration. Motion denied as moot.
